	"Hey guys, Prince of Persia: The Two Thrones is one of my favorite games so I always wanted to make a TAS of this game, this TAS avoids the use of any major glitches and aims to finish the game as fast as possible.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"This is approximately 4 minutes and 35 seconds faster, out of which around 1 minute of timesave comes from newly discovered skips and rest of the improvement was done by better fighting strategies (including bosses), many small skips I was able to find during this TAS.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"The current RTA WR is 1:43:02
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"RTA timing of this TAS is 1:26:56
	$LF
