	"The Promenade:  Current TAS also does the promenade skip here but not optimally, in this skip you first break a furniture item to grab a sand for Dark Prince then you wait for the sand and at the same time you have to do the skip also, so its a bit tricky here because sometimes you get the skip but not sand lol because you escaped too early by doing the skip and that's why its one of my favorite part of this TAS because here you get the sand just one frame before leaving the area.
	$LF
