[div class=p 
	"The Palace Entrance:  Changed the strategy of fight and saved 3 seconds in the end part of the fight, the ending part of this fight is special because here not only you try to kill last four enemies as fast as possible but also try to keep yourself positioned near the gate so that you enter the gate as soon as it opens after all enemies are killed. Later just before elevator skip I found a really cool timesaving trick (RTA viable)...the part where you slide up between walls you can leave analog-up and then jump full 1 second sooner and still grab the fence and survive.
	$LF
