[div class=p 
	"The Well Of Ancestors:  found 2 new skips here and a better version the existing skip all these saved close to 20 seconds I assume, I didn't caompare with older route because those new skips were obviously faster.
	$LF
	"A new skip was also discovered here by PoP speedrunning community it wasn't RTA viable so I was excited to try it out in TAS but sadly it doesn't save time even in PC version so no way its gonna save any time in GC version, actually by performing this skip you become 8.3 seconds ahead initially but then later you have to hit the checpoint then die and restart to load the map to progress ahead so that's where timeloss happens, so I didn't use this skip because its not any faster but slower.
	$LF
